        "source": "autotrader",
        "whyGood": "The E46 325Ci is widely considered one of the best-balanced BMWs ever made. 60K miles on a 2001 is exceptional \u2014 this thing has barely been used. Convertible-specific concerns are manageable: the fabric top on E46s holds up well and the car's mechanicals are proven. No accidents reported. Local at 15 miles.",
